            "text": "Unescaped CSS id interpolated into XPath string literal  [CVSS 5.3: CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N]"
          },
          "locations": [
            {
              "physicalLocation": {
                "artifactLocation": {
                  "uri": "lib/nokogiri/css/xpath_visitor.rb"
                },
